---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BattleCry from '../components/BattleCry.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Organization',
      name: 'Journal Foundation',
      url: 'https://journalfoundation.org',
      publishingPrinciples: 'https://journalfoundation.org/privacy'
    })}
  </script>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <BattleCry>
    <div class="hero-quote">
      <p><strong>Mark Zuckerberg and Elon Musk have their clutches in us</strong>‚Äîtightening the screws while we bleed on the mat.</p>
      <p>Every screen, every algorithm, every "curated" feed is training you to be a biological robot for advertisers.</p>
      <p>When robots come with smiling faces, every 10th sentence an ad‚Äîit's lights out for human free thought and diversity.</p>
      <p><strong>We're building the escape route.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="/docs" class="btn btn--primary">
        üõ†Ô∏è Build Apps
      </a>
      <a href="/learn" class="btn btn--secondary">
        üìö Learn Privacy
      </a>
      <a href="/governance#funding" class="btn btn--tertiary">
        üí∞ Support Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </BattleCry>

  <!-- Three Part Explainer -->
  <section class="explainer-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">We're not building another app. We're building the foundation for digital sovereignty.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="explainer-grid">
        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <div class="explainer-number">1</div>
          <h3>The Problem</h3>
          <p>We're living in a monoculture controlled by algorithmic manipulation:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Facebook feeds controlled by Zuckerberg</li>
            <li>Twitter weaponized by Musk</li>
            <li>TikTok optimizing for addiction</li>
            <li>Every screen training us to be puppets</li>
            <li>The boa constrictor keeps tightening</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <div class="explainer-number">2</div>
          <h3>Why Decentralization Failed</h3>
          <p>Mastodon, Diaspora, Fediverse‚Äîthey decentralized but didn't anonymize:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Metadata still exposed:</strong> Who talks to whom is visible</li>
            <li><strong>Federation centralizes:</strong> Your instance admin sees everything</li>
            <li><strong>Correlation attacks:</strong> Traffic patterns reveal identity</li>
            <li><strong>No plausible deniability:</strong> Encrypted data can be seized</li>
            <li><strong>The China problem:</strong> Download now, decrypt with quantum later</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <div class="explainer-number">3</div>
          <h3>The Stack Difference</h3>
          <p>Infrastructure for sovereignty, not another social network:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Encrypted by default, not optional</li>
            <li>Capability-based sharing (scoped, revocable)</li>
            <li>Metadata minimization through blind relays</li>
            <li>Self-hostable without sacrifice</li>
            <li>Your data in YOUR basement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Urgency -->
  <section class="urgency-section">
    <div class="container urgency-content">
      <h2>The Stakes Are Existential</h2>

      <div class="urgency-quote">
        <p>We're not breathing. We're just getting squeezed.</p>

        <p>All our screens, all the time, giving us algorithmic manipulation. The top 10 on Netflix. The news feeds. Even the music. <strong>It's called the monoculture.</strong></p>

        <p>Right now it's a screen next to us. Soon it's a smiling face‚Äîyour best friend‚Äîand every 10th sentence is an advertisement.</p>

        <p>The hypnotism by robots is coming, whether we act or not.</p>

        <p><strong>If we don't create this free, radical way for humans to have THEIR OWN robots‚Äîthen it's lights out for human free thought and diversity. It's a new dark ages.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <p class="urgency-conclusion">That's why the Journal Protocol Stack exists. That's why this foundation exists.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stack Explainer -->
  <section class="stack-explainer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Journal Protocol Stack</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Three layers that enable apps without platforms</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-grid">
        <div class="stack-layer">
          <h3>üì¶ Layer 1: Vault</h3>
          <p>Encrypted storage you control</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-layer">
          <h3>üîí Layer 2: Cypherlot</h3>
          <p>Capability-based sharing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-layer">
          <h3>üì± Layer 3: Apps</h3>
          <p>Swappable interfaces</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="/stack" class="btn btn--secondary">Learn How It Works ‚Üí</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Get Started -->
  <section class="get-started-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How to Engage</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Three ways to participate</p>
      </div>

      <div class="explainer-grid">
        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <h3>üõ†Ô∏è For Developers</h3>
          <p>Build privacy-first apps on open protocols. No platform required.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Read the specifications</li>
            <li>Try the quickstart guide</li>
            <li>Join technical discussions</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-link">
            <a href="/docs">Start building ‚Üí</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <h3>üìö For Privacy Advocates</h3>
          <p>Understand surveillance, metadata, and why decentralization alone isn't enough.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Learn privacy fundamentals</li>
            <li>Read our whitepapers</li>
            <li>Follow the blog &amp; podcast</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-link">
            <a href="/learn">Visit learning center ‚Üí</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="explainer-card card">
          <h3>üí∞ For Funders &amp; Advisors</h3>
          <p>Support protocol development with radical transparency.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Review financial dashboard</li>
            <li>See governance model</li>
            <li>Contact for partnerships</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-link">
            <a href="/governance">See transparency ‚Üí</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Quote */
  .hero-quote {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(17, 24, 33, 0.85) 0%, rgba(5, 7, 10, 0.85) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-amber);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-xl) auto;
    max-width: min(900px, 100%);
    text-align: left;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-quote p {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hero-quote p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hero-quote strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-emerald);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* CTAs */
  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-group .btn {
    min-width: min(220px, 100%);
  }

  /* Sections */
  section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Explainer Grid */
  .explainer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .explainer-card {
    gap: var(--space-2xs);
    border-color: var(--color-border-subtle);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-base) var(--easing-standard),
      background-color var(--duration-base) var(--easing-standard);
  }

  .explainer-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.4);
    background: rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .explainer-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.45);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-azure);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .explainer-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .explainer-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .explainer-card li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2xs);
    align-items: flex-start;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .explainer-card li strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  /* Urgency Section */
  .urgency-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.7), rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.9));
  }

  .urgency-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .urgency-quote {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-amber);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .urgency-conclusion {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-accent-emerald);
  }

  /* Stack explainer */
  .stack-explainer {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.08), transparent 60%);
  }

  .stack-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .stack-layer {
    border: 1px solid rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.4);
    background: rgba(45, 125, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stack-layer h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Get Started */
  .get-started-section {
    background: rgba(5, 7, 10, 0.55);
  }

  .card-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .card-link a {
    color: var(--color-accent-azure);
  }

  .card-link a:hover,
  .card-link a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--color-accent-emerald);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-quote {
      margin: var(--space-lg);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    }
  }
</style>
